flowchart TD
    A[Sender has plaintext message] --> B[Obtain recipient's public key]
    B --> C[Generate random symmetric session key]
    C --> D[Encrypt message payload\nwith session key via AES]
    C --> E[Encrypt session key\nwith recipient's public key via RSA/ECC]
    D --> F[Bundle: encrypted payload\n+ encrypted session key]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Transmit to recipient]
    G --> H[Recipient receives bundle]
    H --> I[Decrypt session key\nwith private key]
    I --> J{Private key valid?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Recover symmetric session key]
    J -- No --> L[Decryption fails]
    K --> M[Decrypt payload\nwith session key]
    M --> N[Plaintext message recovered]
